# Maximum Security Rules

Project risk tier: **critical**. All rules are mandatory and non-negotiable.

- All external API calls must be audited and logged
- All secrets must use vault integration with rotation
- All database queries must be parameterized — no string interpolation
- Multi-factor authentication required for all admin operations
- Static analysis (SAST) must pass before any merge
- Dependency scanning (SCA) required for every dependency change
- Penetration testing required before production releases
- Zero-trust network access for all service-to-service communication
